					I build websites that actually convert—leveraging <strong class="highlight">AI-driven development</strong> to deliver world-class sites at a fraction of traditional agency costs.
				</p>

				<div class="cta-group">
					<a href="mailto:sayhi@lukaszadam.com" class="cta-button primary">
						<span>Start Your Project</span>
						<svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
					</a>
					<a href="/prices" class="cta-button secondary">View Pricing</a>
				</div>

				<div class="facts-grid">
					<div class="fact-item">
						<Globe size={20} />
						<span>{personalFacts[0].text}</span>
					</div>
					<div class="fact-item">
						<Smartphone size={20} />
						<span>{personalFacts[1].text}</span>
